TEXT: The applicant , Mr PERSON , is a NORP national who was born in DATE and lives in the town of Vinnitsa . ORG ( “ the Government ” ) were represented by their Agent , PERSON .

On DATE the Staromisky District Court of Vinnytsya awarded the applicant CARDINAL NORP hryvnyas ( ORG ) in salary arrears and other payments against the company , ORG AK Sater in which the ORG had had no share since DATE .
The judgment in the applicant ’s favour was not appealed against , became final and GPE ( “ the Bailiffs ” ) instituted enforcement proceedings .
In DATE the applicant instituted civil proceedings in the GPE ORG challenging the GPE inactivity and claiming compensation .
On DATE the court ordered the Bailiffs to enforce the judgment . By the same judgment the court dismissed the applicant ’s claim for compensation .
On DATE ORG dismissed his appeal against that judgment .
The applicant did not appeal in cassation before ORG .
The judgment of DATE remains unenforced .
